\fs36 \cf2 1. Visual Identity & Color Palette\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The visual language is designed to evoke stability, authority, and "optical warmth"\'97balancing the mechanical precision of finance with a human-centric approach.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Primary Palette\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls1\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Deep Trust Blue (\cf3 \cb4 \strokec3 #003B70\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 ):
\f1\b0  The foundational color used for headers, primary navigation, and core branding elements. It conveys financial stability and institutional heritage.\
\ls1\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Action Crimson (\cf3 \cb4 \strokec3 #D11242\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 ):
\f1\b0  A vibrant accent color reserved for specific calls to action (CTAs), navigational "hints," and vital focal points. It symbolizes energy, urgency, and forward motion.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Secondary & UI Palette\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls2\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Institutional Slate (\cf3 \cb4 \strokec3 #0F1632\cf2 \cb1 \strokec2 ):
\f1\b0  Used for high-contrast text and dark-mode background elements.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Premium Cream/Off-White:
\f1\b0  Used as a background alternative to pure white to soften the interface and provide a "luxurious," paper-like feel for wealth reports and advisory content.\
\ls2\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Success Green & Alert Amber:
\f1\b0  Standard functional colors for market data indicators (gains/losses), optimized for high legibility against blue and white backgrounds.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 2. Typography\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The typography system utilizes a 
\f0\b Modern Humanist Sans-Serif
\f1\b0  to ensure clarity across digital interfaces while maintaining a sophisticated, approachable character.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Primary Typeface:
\f1\b0  A custom-weighted sans-serif with open apertures and a humanist structure. (Fallback: 
\f2\i Helvetica Neue
\f1\i0  or 
\f2\i Inter
\f1\i0 ).\
\pard\tx940\tx1440\pardeftab720\li1440\fi-1440\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Headings:
\f1\b0  Bold weights with tight letter spacing for a commanding, authoritative presence.\
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Body Copy:
\f1\b0  Regular weights with generous line-height (1.5x) to ensure readability for long-form market insights.\
\ls3\ilvl1
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Data/Numbers:
\f1\b0  Medium weights with tabular lining to ensure financial figures align perfectly in tables and dashboards.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 3. Language Archetype: "The Global Sage"\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The brand voice functions as a 
\f0\b Trusted Advisor
\f1\b0 \'97knowledgeable, calm, and visionary. It avoids jargon in favor of "sophisticated simplicity."\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Tone:
\f1\b0  Professional, objective, and empowering.\
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Archetype Characteristics:
\f1\b0  * 
\f0\b Authoritative:
\f1\b0  Speaks from a position of global expertise and deep history.\
