\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u9702 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Transparent:
\f1\b0  Clear, direct communication regarding risks and opportunities.\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls4\ilvl0
\f0\b \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Key Phrase Style:
\f1\b0  "Global insights, tailored for your journey." / "Navigating complexity with clarity." / "The power of an integrated perspective."\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 4. UI Elements & Layout\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa320\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs24 \cf2 The interface follows a 
\f0\b Modular Tile Architecture
\f1\b0 , allowing for a responsive experience that scales from mobile wealth-tracking to complex desktop advisory tools.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

\f0\b\fs36 \cf2 Layout Principles\
\pard\tx220\tx720\pardeftab720\li720\fi-720\sa160\partightenfactor0
\ls5\ilvl0
\fs24 \cf2 \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Generous White Space:
\f1\b0  Utilized to prevent "information density fatigue," a common issue in financial apps.\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 The "Horizon" Line:
\f1\b0  Frequent use of horizontal dividers or subtle "arc" elements to guide the eye across data sets, symbolizing a "bridge" to future goals.\
\ls5\ilvl0
\f0\b \kerning1\expnd0\expndtw0 \outl0\strokewidth0 {\listtext	\uc0\u8226 	}\expnd0\expndtw0\kerning0
\outl0\strokewidth0 \strokec2 Information Hierarchy:
\f1\b0  High-level net worth and "Global Market Pulse" are always prioritized at the top of the user\'92s dashboard.\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa160\partightenfactor0

